    "body": "i think i got it to work with my configuration, i put this in my .kshrc \r\n```\r\n\r\nfunction _cd {\r\n\r\n \\cd \"$@\"\r\n\r\n PS1=$(starship prompt | sed 's|%\\\\{||g; s|\\\\}||g; s/%//g' | tr -d '{}')\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\nalias cd=_cd\r\n\r\n\r\ncd \"$PWD\"\r\n\r\n```",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
